<h2>You are logged in <%= current_user.username %>.</h2>

<p>This is where home page where your list of favorite games will be displayed. You can click on the game itself to view its page, edit or delete if need be. Enjoy.</p>

<% if !current_user.games.empty? %>

<h3>Here is your list of favorite games:</h3>

  <% @games.each do |game| %>
  
  <ul>
    <li><p><a href="/games/<%= game.id %>"><strong>"<%= game.name %>"</strong></a></p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <% end %>

  <p><button><a href="/games/new">Add</a></button> a game to your list.</p>

<% else %>

<h3>Oops, looks like you dont have any games. Why don't you add some?</h3>
  <p><button><a href="/games/new">Start</a></button> a list, add your first game.</p>
<% end %>

  <form action="/logout" method="POST">
    <input type="hidden" name="_method" value="DELETE">
    <input type="submit" value="Logout" name="submit">
  </form>